text: Grażyna Różańska (born 27 November 1961) is a Polish rowing cox. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wałcz Category:Sportspeople from West Pomeranian Voivodeship Category:Coxswains (rowing)
